    .guides
      #guide
        h3#guidetitle Fitness Guide
        label(style='margin-left: 37%;') click me!
        a(href='https://drive.google.com/file/d/16R4Innqi2y1RwEpAHBlA0Ae9m4Iml36O/view?usp=sharing')
          img#cover(src='public/resources/imgs/BM-bookCoverAlt.png')
        p#description
          |This book outlines important Health and Fitness topics that is covered in personal training certification courses. I have done the research so you do not have to! There are no workout programs, no biases, only education. It aims to provide you with the knowledge to train yourself and get the results that you desire. No reason to keep trying new things when you can learn how to find a system that works for you and your body. It includes education on exercise and all of Bare Minimum's "Eating Guide" information and a few updates as well. Read the section above for a sneak peek!
        #guidebuttons
          a(href='https://drive.google.com/file/d/16R4Innqi2y1RwEpAHBlA0Ae9m4Iml36O/view?usp=sharing')
            | View
      .review
        #reviews
          #scrollReview
            .reviewBox
              block content
                each val in guideReviews
                  h3.review= val.name
                  p.review= val.review
                  img.rating(src='public/resources/imgs/reviewStar' + val.rating + ".png")
      .submittedQuestions
        #scrollReview
          #submission
            block content
              each val in questions
                p.review= val.submittedquestion
                button.bmbutton(onclick='viewComments(this)', id=val.marker) View Comments
      .feedback
        .newReview
          h3#smallerLabels Leave a Review
          br
          form(action='/processReview', method='post')
            label#smallerText Name
            br
            input#textbox(type='text', name='revieweeName' required)
            br
            label#smallerText Email
            br
            input#textbox(type='email', name='email' required)
            br
            label#smallerText Review
            br
            textarea#largeTextbox(type='text', name='review' required)
            br
            label#smallerText Rating
            select.ratingSelect(type='number' required)
              option(value="1") 1
              option(value="2") 2
              option(value="3") 3
              option(value="4") 4
              option(value="5") 5
            button#bmbutton(type='submit') Submit
        .question
          h3#smallerLabels Ask a fitness question
          br
          form#question(method='post', action='/question')
            label#smallerText Name
            br
            input#textbox(type='text', name='fitname' required)
            br
            label#smallerText Email
            br
            input#textbox(type='email', name='fitemail' required)
            br
            label#smallerText Question
            br
            textarea#largeTextbox(name='fitquestion' required)
            br
            button#bmbutton(type='submit') Ask!
